{
  "bookId": "laozi-heshanggong-wiki",
  "num": 20,
  "title": "第二十章（異俗）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "絕學，"
    },
    {
      "text": "無憂。"
    },
    {
      "text": "唯之與阿，相去幾何。"
    },
    {
      "text": "善之與惡，相去若何。"
    },
    {
      "text": "人之所畏，不可不畏。"
    },
    {
      "text": "荒兮其未央哉！"
    },
    {
      "text": "眾人熙熙，"
    },
    {
      "text": "如享太牢，"
    },
    {
      "text": "如春登臺。"
    },
    {
      "text": "我獨怕兮其未兆，"
    },
    {
      "text": "如嬰兒之未孩。"
    },
    {
      "text": "乘乘兮若無所歸。"
    },
    {
      "text": "眾人皆有餘，"
    },
    {
      "text": "而我獨若遺。"
    },
    {
      "text": "我愚人之心也哉，"
    },
    {
      "text": "沌沌兮。"
    },
    {
      "text": "俗人昭昭，"
    },
    {
      "text": "我獨若昏。"
    },
    {
      "text": "俗人察察，"
    },
    {
      "text": "我獨悶悶。"
    },
    {
      "text": "忽兮若海，"
    },
    {
      "text": "漂兮若無所止。"
    },
    {
      "text": "眾人皆有以，"
    },
    {
      "text": "而我獨頑，"
    },
    {
      "text": "似鄙。"
    },
    {
      "text": "我獨異於人，"
    },
    {
      "text": "而貴食母。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 3
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "絕學不真，不合道文。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 3
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "除浮華則無憂患也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "同為應對而相去幾何。疾時賤質而貴文。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "善者稱譽，惡者諫諍，能相去何如。疾時惡忠直，用邪佞也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人謂道人也。人所畏者，畏不絕學之君也。不可不畏，近令色，殺仁賢。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "或言世俗人荒亂，欲進學為文，未央止也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "熙熙，放淫多情欲也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "如飢思太牢之具，意無足時也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "春，陰陽交通，萬物感動，登台觀之，意志淫淫然。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "我獨怕然安靜，未有情慾之形兆也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "如小兒未能答偶人時也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "我乘乘如窮鄙，無所歸就。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 12,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "眾人餘財以為奢，餘智以為詐。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 13,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "我獨如遺棄，似於不足也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-15",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 14,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不與俗人相隨，守一不移，如愚人之心也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-16",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 15,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "無所分別。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-17",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 16,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "明且達也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-18",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 17,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "如闇昧也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-19",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 18,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "察察，急且疾也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-20",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 19,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "悶悶，無所割截。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-21",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 20,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "我獨忽忽，如江海之流，莫知其所窮極也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-22",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 21,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "我獨漂漂，若飛若揚，無所止也，志意在神域也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-23",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 22,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以，有為也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-24",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 23,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "我獨無為。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-25",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 24,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 3
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "鄙，似若不逮也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-26",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 25,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "我獨與人異也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-27",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 26,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "食，用也。母，道也。我獨貴用道也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
